node.text:
Lots of chocolate 🍫🍫🍫, that’s what I want it right now during the #CircuitBreakerSg period 😋 So, with the ingredients on hand, #callebaut 811 54.5% Dark Chocolate, Cocoa powder and Dark Crispearls, I made into delicious 🍫🎂 I called it a Belgian Chocolate Fantasy Cake. This 🍫🎂 so chocolaty inside and outside 😋😁😆 Now, who wants a slice?!
.
.
Thanks @jimmygoh_bc @callebautchocolate for sharing The Finest Belgian Chocolate 🍫🍫🍫 .
P.S. The chocolates are also available at @phoonhuat stores 😉
.
.
